OL,3,CMan claims he lost job after leaving
OL,4,Cwork early for kidney dialysis
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FA man from Nailsea claims he lost his
OL,8,Fjob at a building site after leaving
OL,9,Fwork early for kidney dialysis
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,FTrevor Maybury, who was employed as a
OL,13,Ftraffic marshall through an agency,
OL,14,Fhad been receiving dialysis for two
OL,15,Fmonths but says he was suddenly told
OL,16,Fhe was being let go at the end of
OL,17,FJanuary.
OL,19,FMr Maybury says he was left shocked
OL,20,Fand in "disbelief".
