OL,3,CMan claims he lost job after leaving
OL,4,Cwork early for kidney dialysis
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FHe said: "Given the opportunity I can
OL,8,Fwork. This is the cruel thing.
OL,10,F"I just want to make a living. Where
OL,11,Fis the compassion?
OL,13,F"I don't normally get emotional but
OL,14,Fit's just ridiculous."
OL,16,FTrevor has been living with chronic
OL,17,Fkidney disease for a number of years
OL,18,Fand started dialysis in December while
OL,19,Fwaiting for a transplant.
