OL,3,CMan claims he lost job after leaving
OL,4,Cwork early for kidney dialysis
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FHe says he began leaving work early
OL,8,Ftwice a week, so he could travel from
OL,9,Fthe building site in Congresbury to
OL,10,FSouth Bristol for treatment.
OL,12,FMr Maybury claims he was told he was
OL,13,Fnot in position when he needed to be
OL,14,Fand he was being replaced.
OL,16,FIt's understood the developer, Bovis
OL,17,FHomes, needs a traffic marshall on
OL,18,Fsite at all times during the working
OL,19,Fday.
OL,21,FIt says Mr Maybury was not an employee.
