OL,3,CMan claims he lost job after leaving
OL,4,Cwork early for kidney dialysis
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FDisability rights lawyer Chris Fry
OL,8,Fsays more should be done to support
OL,9,Fworkers like Trevor, even if they are
OL,10,Femployed through agencies or on zero-
OL,11,Fhours contracts.
OL,13,FMr Fry said: "If someone is disabled.
OL,14,FYou owe them a duty even if they are
OL,15,Fan agency or an employer.
OL,17,F"The upshot is if someone discloses
OL,18,Fthey have a kidney issue which has a
OL,19,Flife changing impact then you have a
OL,20,Fresponsibility to those people to look
OL,21,Fafter them.
