OL,7,F"That's really what the equality act
OL,8,Fsays."
OL,10,FMr Maybury is now hoping to get work
OL,11,Felsewhere. He says he is desperate to
OL,12,Fkeep earning and busy, while he
OL,13,Fmanages his life threatening illness.
